.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, jazz, dubstep, trance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, golf, tennis, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the fan of trance is the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the fan of trance is on the far right##1
4. the fan of jazz is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the fan of dubstep is between the fan of blues and the fan of jazz##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz     | dubstep           | blues | trance  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | weightlifting | golf   | tennis |

