.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, reggae, soul, techno
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, trike, ship, skateboard
1. the fan of reggae is the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the fan of classical##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the fan of classical is between the person driving the taxi and the fan of soul##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | techno   | reggae | classical | soul      |
| Transport     | ship | taxi    | trike  | skateboard |

