.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, tennis, surfing, badminton
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, tram, van, jet-ski
1. the person driving the ship is the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person driving the tram is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person driving the van##2
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | golf | badminton | surfing     | tennis   |
| Transport   | van   | tram     | jet-ski | ship |

