.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, project-manager, accountant, software-developer
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, skateboard, trike, bus
1. the accountant is between the person driving the helicopter and the chef##2
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the chef##1
3. the software-developer is on the right of the chef##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the chef is on the left of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | project-manager | accountant | chef | software-developer |
| Transport   | helicopter         | bus       | skateboard    | trike         |

