.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, eggplant, kale, cherry
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, cycling, skiing, golf
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person eating kale##1
3. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person eating eggplant and the person who's sport is golf##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | cherry   | kale      | eggplant   | mango  |
| Sport   | golf | cycling | skiing | weightlifting |

