.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, pear, corn, spinach
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, mystery, romance, comedy
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person eating pear is between the person eating spinach and the person eating kiwi##2
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | kiwi     | pear | spinach   | corn        |
| Movie-Genre   | western | romance   | mystery | comedy |

