.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, reading, collecting, hiking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, indie, electronic, house
1. the fan of electronic is the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of house##1
3. the fan of blues is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is the fan of indie##1
5. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the fan of indie is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | reading | collecting | hiking | traveling |
| Music-Genre   | electronic          | indie     | house  | blues     |

