3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
4. the software-developer is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | software-developer | entrepreneur | teacher | manager     |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | musical    | thriller   | time-travel |

