3. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the rat and the indonesian##2
4. the owner of the snake is the owner of the snake##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | dutch | indonesian | german | british |
| Pet           | bird  | snake  | hedgehog | rat      |

