The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, surfing, climbing, parkour
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the thai is the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is between the indian and the argentine##2
5. the argentine is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | thai   | indian   | indonesian | argentine |
| Sport         | tennis | surfing | parkour     | climbing    |

