.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games, writing, gardening
4 different pets are kept: hamster, bird, goldfish, fish
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the owner of the hamster and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | writing    | gardening     | filmmaking | board-games |
| Pet     | bird | fish | goldfish       | hamster     |

 